arStrings.szText: "It's eerily quiet down by the docks..."
Eh, outsiders just don’t understand. Everywhere else in Sanctuary, folks thieve and kill and burn. They’ve forgotten the spirits. Not us.
Take what you need, offer what you can. The spirits gift us food, and in turn they take... less necessary things. Memories. Thoughts. A worthy trade for survival, if you ask me.
